  "pc0_js1" -> "pc1_js1" [label="υ ∧ ¬ω ∨ ¬τ ∧ ¬υ ∧ level(r1) ⊐ pc ∨ ¬τ ∧ ¬υ ∧ level(r1) ⊑ pc,\n\
