 obj_level(this) := if υ ∧ hr = P0 then obj_level(this) ⊔ (if this.><r1 then obj_level(r1) else ⊥) ⊔ (if this.><r2 then obj_level(r2) else ⊥) else obj_level(this),\n\
 hr := if υ ∧ hr = P0 then P. else hr}",
